take samples of it. Everyone, we dig as we can. If this is a source of 
energon as strange as it looks, it might give us enough power to 
obliterate the Maximals who came after us! Warhead, terrorize!

He unfolds from his gunship mode and points his torso-mounted laser at 
the ground. He starts firing a continuous beam, effectively working on 
the ground covering the mysterious sphere.

Warhead: Concentrate on my target point! Don't worry about build-up, 
we'll be finished before!
